<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TT4">
<l>kuṇṭilō makkuḻic cōṟṟai vāṅkik kuṟunari tiṉṉa vataṉai muṉṉē</l>
<l>kaṇṭilō meṉṟu kaṉaṉṟu pēykaḷ kaiyaṭit tōṭiṭu kāṭa raṅkā</l>
<l>maṇṭala niṉṟaṅ kuḷāḷa miṭṭu vātittu vīci yeṭutta pāta</l>
<l>maṇṭa muṟanimirn tāṭu meṅka ḷappa ṉiṭantiru vālaṅ kāṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place where our father dances, stretching out so as to reach the cosmic egg</l>
<l>with [his] foot that he forcefully lifted after disputing, placing an Uḷāḷam there, staying in the circle,</l>
<l>as the cremation ground is a stage for demonesses beating [their] hands [and] running,</l>
<l>raging “we don’t see that [anymore] before [us]”,</l>
<l>when the short jackal had dragged [away and] ate the rice from the offering hole in the pit, is Tiruvalaṅkāṭu.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
